title: Valley Of The Gods
description: Great gods Horus and Anubis welcome you to ancient Egypt's best kept secret - Valley Of The Gods. In this mysterious game you re-spin with every win and hit winning combinations to expand your game area while discovering ancient mysteries. Clear the whole area and you invoke ancient incantations, which grant you huge treasures and near immortality in the form of huge multipliers and extra lives. Are you ready for riches beyond the imagination of mortals? Then follow us to Valley Of The Gods!

title: Vikings go to Hell
description: The fearless Vikings are back for their biggest battle yet, as they take on the flaming demon hordes of the underworld! The third instalment of our legendary Vikings series builds on the previous games to bring even more action to the reels - fights for sticky wilds will now also happen in base game, the treasure chests will appear more frequently, and two levels of Free Spins with multipliers allow for truly monstrous wins. Our enraged Nordic warriors invite you to join them on their latest adventure!

title: Vikings Go To Valhalla
description: Will the Hall of Heroes fall, or will the warriors prevail? Vikings Go To Valhalla brings the enraged generals back together in their fourth outing where the ruthless snake king, Jörmungandr looms near, hellbent on destruction. Join Gunnar and his army to protect Asgard with respins and Free Spins where all high paying symbols battle Jörmungandr on every spin. If they win, they turn into Sticky Wilds! Their onslaught continues into the fabled Ragnarök Free Spins where the warriors always win their battles! Collect Rage from high pay wins to fill the Rage meter for up to 20 respins with any one Viking always winning their battle with the beast. The treasury of the kings is on players’ side too with a Treasure chest that can land on the 5th reel to award an array of exciting prizes!

title: Vikings Go Wild
description: Join The Vikings on a mysterious adventure across the dark blue ocean and slay the sea monster in Free Spin mode, which turns the victorious vikings into sticky wilds!Players will enjoy joining The Vikings on their adventure across the raging ocean, slaying the sea monster in Free Spin mode and turning the victorious heroes into sticky wilds.The treasure chest offers a mystery win and a chance to trigger even more Free Spins.A medium to high volatility game which focuses on the extraordinary opportunity to Get sticky wilds for the entire Free Spin round.

title: Vikings Go Berzerk
description: The Vikings are back in a feature packed sequel. The core mechanics are untouched - the Vikings go Wild in the free spin mode, this time by defeating mythological siren creatures.The Vikings can go Berzerk, meaning they will ALWAYS defeat the siren and turn into a wild. By filling the rage collections in the base game, the player is awarded with a Free Spin sessions where 1 Viking is Berzerk.In the  Free Spin Mode, all 4 vikings go berzerk and will reward the player legendary wins!

title: Brazil Bomba
description: There's no party like the carnival in Rio de Janeiro. Players join in the fun with our avalanche gameBrazil Bomba where symbols cascade down the reels and every 6 symbol diagonal cluster brings awin. Anything can happen in this magical place!

title: Holmes and the Stolen Stones
description: Five Jackpots are up for grabs in this action packed adventure with Mr Holmes. Follow him to search for the missing stones and enter the warehouse bonus game to collect stones to increase your chances in the Free Spin jackpot game.A low to medium variance game which focuses on Frequent jackpot wins and a Shard collection feature. You are never far away from the next Jackpot Free spins.

title: Golden Fishtank
description: Join the exciting and action packed adventure with the fish that live and prosper in Golden Fishtank.In Golden Fishtank the players will participate in an experience that revolves around the exciting and adrenaline packed Free Spins. When the player manages to enter free spins 18 objects from the bottom of the tank come to life for the player to pick from. Inside each of the objects there is a feature hidden which the player will keep for the entire duration of Free Spins.Play Golden Bet feature to get 1 additional feature pick if you would enter the free spin mode. A Golden Bet spin cost 25 cost instead of 20.

title: Golden Fish Tank 2 Gigablox
description: A sequel to poular Golden Fish Tank, new installation brigs what's best about part 1 while adding Yggdrasil's Gigablox to the mix for even more amazing feature combos. Game is set in the same environment as the original (aquarium), and features the core Free Spins with special features chosen in Pick and Click game, with new possible bonuses. New addition - bonus chest - gets players even more surprise wins.

title: Bounty Pop
description: Here comes BountyPop! A new game in the POP-ular PopWins franchise from Avatar UX.BountyPop comes packed with expanding reels, random multipliers, free spins, and three BonusWheels. Boom! The PopWins series center around the PopWins feature, where symbols pop upona symbol win, and reels expand with each win. If they grow high enough (6 high), the Bonus Wheelwill award a random multiplier. There are one Bonus Wheel in the base game and three levels ofBonus Wheels at specific heights in the free spins mode. Let's get poppin'!

title: Tut's Twister
description: The peace of King Tut has been disturbed and now he's risen from his tomb, wreaking havoc across the reels in Tut's Twister! Hit two wilds and Tut will transform one into a wild sandstorm, creating a reel-tall column of wilds! This wild vortex will continue to consume wilds on the reels, awarding respins and a multiplier as it grows out of control. After finally disintegrating, King Tut will unleash all absorbed wilds back on the reels for epic win potential! Use single wilds to collect ancient hieroglyphics, unlocking Tut's hidden curses and unleashing twisters of overwhelming power! Let this ancient ruler's anger pave your way to legendary riches and join the army of King Tut's win-hungy zealots!
